37babaca-fbfb-4b9d-917e-529b4017b072.do_description: To make the output, you have to...bottom three by three blocks are the three by three from the two blocks from the top
37babaca-fbfb-4b9d-917e-529b4017b072.grid_description: The output grid size...same size with three by three at bottom of it
37babaca-fbfb-4b9d-917e-529b4017b072.see_description: In the input, you should see...one color on black background

5c72eb71-3fcb-4ba8-b05f-46140a5be89e.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the original grid to the top 66% of the output grid. Then ignore the top two rows of the grid, copy the next three rows, and paste them into the bottom 33% of the output grid. Change all of the blue blocks to the red-orange color
5c72eb71-3fcb-4ba8-b05f-46140a5be89e.grid_description: The output grid size....s 33% bigger than the input grid
5c72eb71-3fcb-4ba8-b05f-46140a5be89e.see_description: In the input, you should see...A grid with a pattern in blue blocks

876aa2c8-de2f-478c-b3f8-6933dff1e55f.do_description: To make the output, you have to...change the color and add one third potion
876aa2c8-de2f-478c-b3f8-6933dff1e55f.grid_description: The output grid size...should be one third to the original box
876aa2c8-de2f-478c-b3f8-6933dff1e55f.see_description: In the input, you should see...some colored boxes

94911e6c-cbea-45f0-8b76-e1a717dab0d0.do_description: To make the output, you have to...make a replica of the design in the input grid and make sure you fill all the grid because the output grid is 3 by 9 while the input grid is 3 by 6
94911e6c-cbea-45f0-8b76-e1a717dab0d0.grid_description: The output grid size...change it to 3 by 9
94911e6c-cbea-45f0-8b76-e1a717dab0d0.see_description: In the input, you should see...black background designed with blue grid

99c37804-4beb-4a44-8171-f9ff8494ffb2.do_description: To make the output, you have to....change the size of the grid, start in the top left corner with black, then red, and then black.  Continue to make a checkerboard pattern to fill in the all the squares.
99c37804-4beb-4a44-8171-f9ff8494ffb2.see_description: In the input, you should see....two checkerboard shapes, one with black and blue squares and the other one with red and black squares.

9feb2736-073d-4364-bd5e-912c35557199.do_description: To make the output, you have to...continue the pattern with additional 3x3 squares on the bottom
9feb2736-073d-4364-bd5e-912c35557199.see_description: In the input, you should see...3x6 pattern with blue and black pattern.

b2478896-682c-4450-8e5b-4b9d735c1a98.do_description: To make the output, you have to...after change grid size use the same pattern but change the color into red, assume the design is in 3x9 grid
b2478896-682c-4450-8e5b-4b9d735c1a98.grid_description: The output grid size... change into 3x9
b2478896-682c-4450-8e5b-4b9d735c1a98.see_description: In the input, you should see...colored grid in with black grid

b7ebed9d-1ad2-4be5-879b-7146ca1659f7.do_description: To make the output, you have to...resize or copy paste the color grid as in the input grid
b7ebed9d-1ad2-4be5-879b-7146ca1659f7.grid_description: The output grid size...the size in the input grid
b7ebed9d-1ad2-4be5-879b-7146ca1659f7.see_description: In the input, you should see...the black and color grid

f8344fbf-a9db-4dec-b0ea-4eae7cdc310c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...keep the original pattern, change the blue to red, and then continue the pattern in the new 3 rows.
f8344fbf-a9db-4dec-b0ea-4eae7cdc310c.grid_description: The output grid size...add 3 rows to the bottom.
f8344fbf-a9db-4dec-b0ea-4eae7cdc310c.see_description: In the input, you should see...a grid that is 3x6 with black and blue.

f8e06370-f89e-469f-a37f-cebf57bd916a.do_description: To make the output, you have to... change blue to red.
f8e06370-f89e-469f-a37f-cebf57bd916a.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input.
